            "title": "盤中速報 - 合正(5381)股價拉至漲停，漲停價33.45元，成交8,737張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>合正(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5381:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5381\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5381-TW</a>)20日09:15上漲3元，股價漲停報33.45元，委買12,000張、委賣564,000張，成交8,737張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為變壓器。印刷電路板及其耗材。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>合正(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5381:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5381\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5381-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲18.95%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.98%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+3,687 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+3,686 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
